Abstract = {This paper introduces a novel approach to enhance Retrieval-Augmented
   Generation (RAG) systems by integrating Text-Representing Centroid (TRC)
   methodology. Addressing the limitations of traditional vector databases,
   this method preserves structural relationships and adapts to content
   complexity, improving information retrieval efficiency and accuracy. Key
   contributions include advanced graph construction, relevance scoring
