Abstract = {Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) is starting to be used in
   professional settings like the legal domain. In classic information
   retrieval (IR) systems, the effectiveness of the system is often
   evaluated using measures that rely on relevance judgements. Van Opijnen
   and Santos {[}1] have created a framework of relevance for information
   retrieval systems for legal professionals, to ground these evaluation
