   of the NFDI4DataScience Gateway, employing a Retrieval Augmented
   Generation-based (RAG) approach. The NFDI4DS Gateway, as a foundational
   framework, offers a unified and intuitive interface for querying various
   scientific databases using federated search. The RAG-based scholarly QA,
   powered by a Large Language Model (LLM), facilitates dynamic interaction
