   Telecommunications; Xi'an Jiaotong University; Changsha University},
Abstract = {There are various forms of military knowledge and intelligence,
   including text, audio, images, videos and other modalities. Traditional
   knowledge representation methods cannot effectively associate and fuse
   these knowledge and intelligence, but with the rapid development of
   large language models based on retrieval augmentation generation
   technology, they have been able to identify and process multimodal
   information, so on this basis, this paper aims to realize the
   association representation of knowledge through the retrieval and
   multimodal processing capabilities provided by retrieval augmentation
   generation technology, build a vector database for multimodal
   battlefield intelligence knowledge, provide efficient storage and
   retrieval capabilities, and effectively associate and fuse battlefield
   knowledge to achieve effective battlefield multimodal Knowledge fusion
